16:T54b,Tracy is soul guide and mentor, energetic interpreter, and international facilitator based on the Kohala Coast. She is given to empowering souls deeply landed in matter and honoring the multitude of realities and expressions of love within each of us. Tracy has spent the last decade immersed in both study and practice within traditions of healing and integration, energetic mastery, and soul initiation. She combines lived experience, years of training and depth of study with intuitive adeptness and precise energetic attunement in her work. 

Tracy's soul mentorship is focused on midwifing souls into embodied depth and well being.  Her one on one practice welcomes individuals and couples and covers the following:
-Emotional fluency
-Nervous system regulation and stabilization
-Neuroplasticity training
-Relational wellness
-Erotic embodiment
-Practical integration for soulful living
-Clearing patterns and behaviors that inhibit wellness and radiance

Tracy's group work focuses on supporting fields of vibratory coherence between humans and building group capacity for generative healing , creativity, and collaboration. This work is deeply supportive for organizations, collectives, and any group wanting to understand relational dynamics to support generative and resourcing environments. Reach out directly to find out more about group work.14:["$","$L15",null,{"islandSlug":"big-island","islandDisplayName":"Big Island","modalitySlug":"meditation","modalityName":"Meditation","practitioners":[{"id":"63c17020-1b66-480a-8bc5-eb80d7ed5ef9","name":"Somatic Therapy","title":"$undefined","businessName":"$undefined","image":"https://sccksxvjckllxlvyuotv.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/practitioner-images/practitioners/1774573523320-uz5q8ciqyir.webp","type":"practitioner","modality":"Somatic Therapy, Breathwork, Trauma-Informed Care, Soul Guidance, Nervous System Regulation, Meditation, Craniosacral, Energy Healing","modalities":["Somatic Therapy","Breathwork","Trauma-Informed Care","Soul Guidance","Nervous System Regulation","Meditation","Craniosacral","Energy Healing"],"sessionType":"in_person","acceptsNewClients":true,"bio":"Somatic Therapy, Somatic Experiencing, IFS Internal Family Systems, Akashic Records Readings, Somatic Bodywork, CranialSacral, Past Life Regression in South Kona online and in-person.","location":"Captain Cook","rating":5,"lat":19.420526,"lng":-155.884115,"tier":"free","externalBookingUrl":"$undefined","island":"big_island","updatedAt":"2026-04-02T09:57:41.456979+00:00","verified":false},{"id":"f75b67df-0803-4b53-8259-56255e3c7b20","name":"Dana Forrest","title":"$undefined","businessName":"Island Oasis Holistic","image":"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/cc4a6b_422e4c9f634e4e3baf99498185593534%7Emv2.png/v1/fit/w_2500,h_1330,al_c/cc4a6b_422e4c9f634e4e3baf99498185593534%7Emv2.png","type":"practitioner","modality":"Alternative Therapy, Meditation, Sound Healing","modalities":["Alternative Therapy","Meditation","Sound Healing"],"sessionType":"in_person","acceptsNewClients":true,"bio":" Island Oasis Holistic provides a safe, sacred space that enables our clients to explore their wellness journey through Sound Healing, Meditation, and Self-inquiry. Each person is the expert of their own life and has the innate capacity for strength, resilience, creativity, and well-being. ","location":"Hilo","rating":5,"lat":19.725238,"lng":-155.086221,"tier":"free","externalBookingUrl":"","island":"big_island","updatedAt":"2026-04-02T09:31:30.328449+00:00","verified":false},{"id":"af8f72f6-1611-4f4e-9080-f0fc0ce1d530","name":"Gloria  Baraquio","title":"$undefined","businessName":"$undefined","image":"http://static1.squarespace.com/static/53d82867e4b0d4d3dfed83e3/t/68b53cef249f594a002cba21/1757002433699/FUJI0973.webp?format=1500w","type":"practitioner","modality":"Yoga, Meditation, Counseling, Life Coaching","modalities":["Yoga","Meditation","Counseling","Life Coaching"],"sessionType":"in_person","acceptsNewClients":true,"bio":"Discover Shivakali Yoga with Gloria, offering personalized yoga retreats, teacher training, and spiritual counseling to help you find clarity, peace, and purpose in your life’s journey.","location":"Pahoa","rating":5,"lat":19.526165,"lng":-154.98475,"tier":"free","externalBookingUrl":"$undefined","island":"big_island","updatedAt":"2026-04-02T09:57:42.071957+00:00","verified":false},{"id":"8b3b475b-277d-405e-a450-e2a6bf96e14d","name":"Radhe Hendrickson","title":"$undefined","businessName":"$undefined","image":"https://sccksxvjckllxlvyuotv.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/practitioner-images/1959462e8165144883d6223b0cda8b67.jpg","type":"practitioner","modality":"Yoga, Meditation","modalities":["Yoga","Meditation"],"sessionType":"in_person","acceptsNewClients":true,"bio":"Radhe first practiced yoga as a freshman in college upon the recommendation of her father. She was classically trained in ballet as a child so it was an easy transition for her to make. F